EigenMeat.EigenMaze
Class Mesh

java.lang.Object
  EigenMeat.EigenMaze.Mesh
All Implemented Interfaces:
Drawable
public class Mesh
extends java.lang.Object
implements Drawable

A Mesh contains vertex and triangle data of a three-dimensional object suitable for drawing into the engine. A game entity is usually represented by a Mesh.

translate

public EigenMeat.EigenMaze.Triangle[] translate(float x,
                                                float y,
                                                float z)
Copies and translates all Triangles in the mesh by the specified amounts. Meshes are usually centered at (0,0,0); this will return an array of triangles centered at (x,y,z).

Parameters:
x - the x shift to apply to each triangle.
y - the y shift to apply to each triangle.
z - the z shift to apply to each triangle.
Returns:
the shifted array of Triangles.
